<b>Kamazo</b>

598
00:27:40.760 --> 00:27:43.240
<b>"the Reaper"</b>

599
00:27:44.760 --> 00:27:49.020
Zorojuro, why would you
wanna help that woman?

600
00:27:51.140 --> 00:27:54.270
Why do you wanna slash her?

601
00:27:54.270 --> 00:27:59.530
I'm only after the brat
that won't stop laughing.

602
00:28:04.570 --> 00:28:07.080
Don't worry, Toko.

603
00:28:08.040 --> 00:28:09.790
Kamzo the Reaper.

604
00:28:10.250 --> 00:28:15.300
You're known as an indiscriminate street
slasher in the capital, but in actuality...

605
00:28:15.300 --> 00:28:18.170
you're Orochi's assassin
disguised as an outlaw!

606
00:28:18.590 --> 00:28:22.380
Why else would you be after Otoko?

607
00:28:22.380 --> 00:28:26.350
I see you don't address
the shogun by his title.

608
00:28:26.350 --> 00:28:28.970
Who are you anyway?

609
00:28:30.980 --> 00:28:33.980
Lord Samurai, please help us!

610
00:28:35.150 --> 00:28:42.450
Well, of course, I'm not gonna just stand here
and watch a kid and a woman get killed...

611
00:28:42.450 --> 00:28:43.950
I will repay you any way I can!

612
00:28:45.620 --> 00:28:47.540
I wouldn't mind some food and sake.

613
00:28:48.200 --> 00:28:49.370
Done.

614
00:28:51.370 --> 00:28:53.620
Alright! Deal!

615
00:29:00.170 --> 00:29:05.930
Fine by me. I've been authorized
to kill anyone that gets in my way.

616
00:29:08.300 --> 00:29:12.730
Taking out lackeys like you
usually upsets the boss.

617
00:29:12.730 --> 00:29:15.020
Don't worry!

618
00:29:15.020 --> 00:29:18.150
You're the one that's gonna die!

619
00:30:00.440 --> 00:30:02.530
He's pretty tough!

620
00:30:47.400 --> 00:30:49.820
Looks like you're getting serious.

621
00:31:25.900 --> 00:31:29.650
Still feels like something's missing.

622
00:31:41.620 --> 00:31:44.420
I'm beary hungry!

623
00:31:44.420 --> 00:31:50.840
If I beat Straw Hat, can you bear
to give me all the prisoners' dumplings?

624
00:31:50.710 --> 00:31:53.140
<b>Bearman
Bear SMILE Fruit
A Gifter</b>

625
00:31:53.140 --> 00:31:55.930
Sure. Go wild!

626
00:31:55.930 --> 00:31:58.560
That's beary Queen of you!

627
00:31:58.560 --> 00:32:01.390
This bear's a hundred times
more motivated now!

628
00:32:01.390 --> 00:32:02.980
What?!

629
00:32:02.980 --> 00:32:05.060
Let's bear it and go!

630
00:32:11.070 --> 00:32:12.410
Bear!

631
00:32:17.790 --> 00:32:20.040
Those punches...

632
00:32:20.040 --> 00:32:22.170
bearly hurt!

633
00:32:25.460 --> 00:32:26.670
Sir Straw Hat!

634
00:32:27.130 --> 00:32:30.470
He might look adorable, but he's still a bear!

635
00:32:30.470 --> 00:32:35.640
They say that a bear's claws are
sharp enough to rip humans limb from limb!

636
00:32:35.640 --> 00:32:37.510
Be careful!

637
00:32:39.100 --> 00:32:40.890
Bear!

638
00:32:43.690 --> 00:32:44.690
Send him flying...

639
00:32:45.730 --> 00:32:47.230
without making contact!

640
00:33:02.830 --> 00:33:07.840
Damn, when I put power behind it,
I end up hitting them anyway!

641
00:33:08.380 --> 00:33:11.800
What are you...

642
00:33:11.800 --> 00:33:14.430
attempting to do?

643
00:33:14.430 --> 00:33:15.680
Forget it.

644
00:33:16.380 --> 00:33:17.510
Let's keep going!

645
00:33:18.140 --> 00:33:19.310
Next!

646
00:34:10.020 --> 00:34:12.530
Wide open!

647
00:34:43.560 --> 00:34:44.850
I can't pull it out!

648
00:34:56.280 --> 00:34:58.950
I'll make do with this for now...

649
00:35:11.960 --> 00:35:13.500
Three...

650
00:35:14.210 --> 00:35:16.050
swords?!

651
00:35:21.800 --> 00:35:23.680
Three-Sword Style!

652
00:35:27.100 --> 00:35:28.730
Purgatory...

653
00:35:37.230 --> 00:35:40.150
Oni Giri!

654
00:36:13.850 --> 00:36:16.770
How fearsome...

655
00:36:26.330 --> 00:36:29.910
Damn... This isn't even the final battle!

656
00:37:05.070 --> 00:37:07.910
L-Lord Samurai!
